<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #cb1d20;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 25px;
        }
        .email-body h2 {
            color: #cb1d20;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .email-body p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .email-body .order-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
        }
        .email-body .order-details ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .email-body .order-details ul li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-body .order-details ul li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f1f3f5;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #cb1d20;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #cb1d20;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #b41a1d;
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }
        .tracking-info {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .tracking-info p {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            Order Confirmation
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h2>Hello <%= user.name %>!</h2>
            <p>Thank you for your order! We are delighted to confirm your purchase. Below are the details:</p>

            <div class="order-details">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %></li>
                    <li><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= orderDate %></li>
                    <li><strong>Shipping Address:</strong> <%= shippingAddress %></li>
                    <li><strong>Items:</strong>
                        <ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 15px;">
                            <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                                <li><%= item.name %> - Quantity: <%= item.quantity %>, Price: $<%= item.price %></li>
                            <% }); %>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Shipping Amount:</strong> $<%= shipping %></li>
                    <li><strong>Total Amount:</strong> $<%= totalAmount %></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <a href="<%= redirectlink %>" class="cta-button">View My Orders</a>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to <a href="#">contact us</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Ayoob.ecom . All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

